Also, what is the mana cost for the spells?  I believe superior healing is around 250 mana a shot right now?  So these would probably be around 500 or better?  Keep them at a high mana cost, and I don't think anyone will argue too much.<br>
<br>
Now then, a higher version of bard mez?  Sounds good to me.  Of course I'm a bard.  Does that mean enchies are angry now too?  hehehe<br>
